{"type": "article", "id": 7229, "title": "Cole Haan 和 Todd Snyder 合作男鞋", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-10T07:53:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234149089VLHtGxInKris3.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t男装品牌 Todd Snyder 和做鞋子的 Cole Haan 合作推出了一个 2015 春季男鞋系列。这个系列中包括麻底布面便鞋，牛津皮鞋，loafers鞋，马球靴等六种鞋型，以奶白色和棕褐色为主。这些鞋子的特点在于配上西装可以穿去办公室，而换上牛仔裤，你就可以穿着它们去登山或是运动。这些鞋子大多在200-300美元之间，<a href=\"http://www.colehaan.com/mens-whats-new-toddsnyder\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>或是<a href=\"http://www.toddsnyder.com/collections/shoes\" target=\"_blank\">这里都可以线上购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234147ZEhwQDxBtH3cmK4J.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.67356688\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234147GMC5Tsj0Bq81gaVA.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.67356688\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523414831QTBcDsPREANHWm.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.67356688\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052341489YctOW5ENKLDXA18.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.67356688\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}